# Google OAuth 2.0 — Desktop app client (RONY-6)
#
# Create these at https://console.cloud.google.com :
#   1. Create/select a project.
#   2. APIs & Services → Enable APIs → enable "Gmail API".
#   3. APIs & Services → OAuth consent screen → External → add your Google
#      account under "Test users" (keeps you out of the verification queue).
#   4. APIs & Services → Credentials → Create credentials → OAuth client ID
#      → Application type: "Desktop app".
#   5. Copy the Client ID and Client secret below.
#
# Then: copy this file to ".env" (which is gitignored) and fill in real values.

GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your-client-id.apps.googleusercontent.com
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=your-client-secret
